Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:11.75,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}未知なる方ヘ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.74,0:01:16.96,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}沸き上がる情熱と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.08,0:01:21.89,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}燻る魂が胸を締め付ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:26.54,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}燃える緋の様に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:29.02,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}There I'll find my place
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:32.59,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Under the rader I'm reaching for the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:39.08,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}鋼の牙を起て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:47.66,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}呻きと聲を挙げ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:54.82,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I'm gonna live out my life untamed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:17.65,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}たった―つのこの身焦がして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:22.92,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}血が枯れはてるまで進む
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:32.32,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}遠い空から反る光もこの身に當たり消え
